text: Saint-Germain-en-Laye () is a commune in the Yvelines department in the Île- de-France in north-central France. On 1 January 2019, the former commune of Fourqueux was merged into Saint-Germain-en-Laye.Arrêté préfectoral 19 December 2018 ==References== Category:Communes in Yvelines Category:Subprefectures in France
title: Saint-Germain-en-Laye
